### Get Profile
GET http://localhost:3000/auth/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Refresh Token
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/refresh
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Validate Token
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/validate
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}} 